snippet.title: Sub Rosa Cinematic Early Access Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase
snippet.description:
Sub Rosa is a multiplayer first-person shooter about tense deals, double-crosses, and the occasional high-speed car chase.

Sub Rosa is in Early Access right now if you want to play it.
